description: Proxy startup
When the proxy tries to startup.

event.Summary: SIP proxy is trying to start

description: Successfull Proxy startup
The proxy is now successfully startup. Normally this means that the proxy is in service. In rare cases (e.g. binding has been failed) network is not alive.

event.Summary: SIP proxy started up successfully

description: Proxy Shutdown inititated
Fired when the proxy got a signal that it should be shut down (e.g. service sipproxyd stop)

event.Summary: SIP proxy shutdown has been initiated
